cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NA

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image reconstruction and texture details.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also likely as the paper discusses compressed sensing and its application in image reconstruction.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper proposes an adaptive graph-based TV method.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possibility as the paper deals with image reconstruction from limited and noisy data.
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is a possibility as the paper proposes a new algorithm for tomographic reconstructions.
